      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      rr-cod-mas           to   w-let-arc-zcn-mas      .
           move      rr-cod-con           to   w-let-arc-zcn-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-zcn-000      thru let-arc-zcn-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Memorizzazione descrizione          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        rr-cod-con           =    zero
                     move  "Tutti"        to   rr-cod-con-des
           else      move  w-let-arc-zcn-des
                                          to   rr-cod-con-des         .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Visualizzazione conto               *
