           move      zero                 to   rr-cod-con             .
           move      spaces               to   rr-cod-con-des         .
           perform   vis-cod-con-000      thru vis-cod-con-999        .
           perform   vis-des-con-000      thru vis-des-con-999        .
       acc-cod-mas-600.
